txt.en: Defeat the Master of the Fane
Defeat the Master of the Fane
A terrible gaunt-man oversees the vile rituals of necromancy at Aufaltor, the Fane of the Eye.
The Master of the Fane's body falls broken upon the black stones of Aufaltor

Within Aufaltor, the Fane of the Eye, lurks a vile master of the Dead.

Through foul necromancy, a terrible gaunt-man of the Elder Days raises the wights of Aufaltor into servitude. If Nidhlas' company had the misfortune to come to Aufaltor, their fates may well be bound to the will of the Master of the Fane.

You should defeat the Master of the Fane.
The Master of the Fane can be found at Aufaltor in Thuringwath.\n\nYou should defeat the Master of the Fane.
Defeat the Master of the Fane at Aufaltor.

You have defeated the Master of the Fane and put an end to the necromantic rites being performed at Aufaltor.
